Relative + Absolute XPathtr

/html/body/dev[1]/div[2]/ul/li[1]/a/b

combination

//ul[contains(@id,'main menu')]/li/a/b
//ul[contains(@id,'main menu')]//b

//table[@id='resultTable']/tbody/tr/td/input[@type='checkbox']
//table[@id='resultTable']//input[@type='checkbox']

................................................................................  
      
      
      
                               XPATH AXES for traverse

Syntax

//XPath//following::tagname
//XPath//preceding::tagname


Match all elements after manda
//div[text()='manda user']//following::*

Match all elements before manda
//div[text()='manda user']//preceding::*

Match with the 1st input after password
//*[text()='Password']//following::input[1]

Find first dropdown after User role
//*[text()='User role']//following::select[1]

Find first input tag after Confirm Password
//*[text()='Confirm Password']//following::input[1]

Find first dropdown after Status
//*[text()='Status']//following::select[1]

To reach parent node
Syntax:    //parent::tagname
                  or
                  //..
                  
To reach child node
Syntax:   //child::tagname
                  or
                  /
                  
................................................................................               
                  
                              CSS Selector
                  
Text function is not present
Trverse is back direction not allowed

Id
  #
  
Class
  .
  
Contains
  *
  
Starts with 
  ^
  
Ends with
  $
  
  
Examples
   #email1         - it will find all the element which has id email1
   input#email1    - it will find the input tag which has a id email1
   
Synatx 
   tagname[attribute='value']      
   input[name='email1']              Css
         or
   //input[@name='email1']           XPath

Input button
   input[button='txtusername']
   
   input[id^='txtusername']
   input[id$='txtusername']
   input[id*='txtusername']
   
   div[class='orangehrm-login-footer-sm']
         or
   div.orangehrm-login-footer-sm
   
   
   div[class='orangehrm-login-footer-sm'] a
   
   div[class='orangehrm-login-footer-sm'] a
   
   div[class='orangehrm-login-footer-sm'] a:nth-child(2)
   div[class='orangehrm-login-footer-sm'] a:first-child
   
   div[class='orangehrm-login-footer-sm'] a:nth-of-type(2)
   
